      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 382: Same controller reinitialization bug exists in start(): resetting bwController_ without clearing bwControllerInitialized_ leaves the controller target at the default bitrate for subsequent starts. Apply the same fix here so setupVideoBitrateInfo() can sync with codecVideo-\u003ebitrate again.\n```suggestion\n        bwController_.reset();\n        bwControllerInitialized_ \u003d false;\n```",
      "revId": "5597f66cc7a60003d0c0a64d92a941072d897385",
